\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec3 As our database grows, calculating this full\'a0 U_hat\'d7p_hat\uc0\u8203 \'a0 formula for every single user-job pair will eventually become a massive computation and latency bottleneck. My optimal suggestion here is use a 
\f1\b two-stage recommendation funnel
\f0\b0  to maintain scalability:\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\qj\partightenfactor0
