\f1\b \cb2 Stage 0: Database Retrieval & Hard Filters:\'a0\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 Before we load any data into memory for ML scoring, we must push as much filtering down to the database layer as possible.
\f2\fs24 \
